  <brief_title>Acupuncture Combined With Pulmonary Rehabilitation: Are There Additional Benefits?</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Impact of Acupuncture as an Adjunct to Pulmonary Rehabilitation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
